{"tid":695094,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有幾多人寧願租都唔買樓","createTime":"2018-06-09T03:04:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-09T12:42:35.000Z","uid":116709,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"fd563862fe8a87d01211ad4ef1cdfd3d009bc583","tid":695094,"uid":116709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T03:04:08.000Z","msg":"博樓價跌賺差價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bda7cf82516bcdd930d1b5f7720ff3ac6ad5d0a","tid":695094,"uid":68556,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T03:10:21.000Z","msg":"租樓其實好着數<br />\n<br />\n唔洗供樓捱貴利息差餉地租管理費維修;<br />\n又可以一年去幾次旅行，日日fine dining，有生活態度，<br />\n唔洗驚失業有病斷供;<br />\n唔洗驚樓爆做負資產俾銀行call loan;<br />\n又可以俾人笑做樓奴，<br />\n又可以投資用股息交租做股神。<br />\n<br />\n每年轉去租唔同嘅新盤，<br />\n定期轉換下環境，<br />\n租樓真係日日賺。  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08d76b1b562e8b31aaf758aeeac63f78e36e9a64","tid":695094,"uid":86097,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T03:12:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c776222b74828f163ba967fe5d9f2c3fef802580","tid":695094,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T03:15:00.000Z","msg":"絕望死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">居屋成交價近1000萬！林一鳴：每天幻想樓價大跌的人 真是絕望死！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n居屋也直逼千萬，資深地產分析員林一鳴表示，現在樓市升極都唔識停，樓價升到痴咗線，最主要是「而家唔買，遲D買重貴」的心態，就算今天摸頂都要入市。這是一種「希望變絕望」的心態，當初有很多人以為政府辣招可以壓制樓價，加上高官的不斷提醒樓市風險高，樓價已超出市民負擔能力（當時新界上車盤還是二百萬元，高官就開始提醒了），息口很快上升等，令到一班人期待樓價下跌，甚至將自住樓賣出。<br />\n<br />\n但到了現在，這些人都變得絕望了；辣招越壓樓價越升，銀行一直不加息，土地供應專責小組搞了半年，更令人相信政府根本冇能力搵地，結果心態開始變得絕望，如果而家唔買居屋，遲些可能連公屋都買唔起，於是破頂都要入市。<br />\n<br />\n他又指，特別是辣招剛推出時賣樓轉租的人，交了幾年貴租，現在同一筆錢買細一半面積都不夠，過去五六年每天幻想樓價大跌，最近真是絕望死了，相信大家身邊都有很多這樣的人，當時賣樓的錢，今天在樓下買車位都不夠，心情真是好痛苦。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180608/58294467\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180608%2F58294467&d=RXqriQOFW%2F1LyN3qRmJbrcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=97a48dd1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180608%2F58294467&h=2cb12fa6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180608/58294467</a>"},{"pid":"c3b982779e2c2eb27755428400c199203230cc5f","tid":695094,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"08d76b1b562e8b31aaf758aeeac63f78e36e9a64","tid":695094,"uid":86097,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"1bda7cf82516bcdd930d1b5f7720ff3ac6ad5d0a","tid":695094,"uid":68556,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T03:10:21.000Z","msg":"租樓其實好着數<br />\n<br />\n唔洗供樓捱貴利息差餉地租管理費維修;<br />\n又可以一年去幾次旅行，日日fine dining，有生活態度，<br />\n唔洗驚失業有病斷供;<br />\n唔洗驚樓爆做負資產俾銀行call loan;<br />\n又可以俾人笑做樓奴，<br />\n又可以投資用股息交租做股神。<br />\n<br />\n每年轉去租唔同嘅新盤，<br />\n定期轉換下環境，<br />\n租樓真係日日賺。  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T03:12:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T03:15:58.000Z","msg":"不斷加租, 仲可以令你發奮向上<br />\n<br />\n生活過得充實, 唔會變廢青<br />\n<br />\n利申：廢青"},{"pid":"9533b511026cac1018b4eb63d031125ce7e722a8","tid":695094,"uid":128600,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T03:39:30.000Z","msg":"希望大家一齊唔好買樓，租樓好啦～<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：比租租供養中"},{"pid":"c5e0cedb444ba37591c23552fe961b65f9741a61","tid":695094,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T03:40:29.000Z","msg":"租樓日日賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1261579e2d2cc617a434a7f1ab97643bb83e0a60","tid":695094,"uid":180348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T03:45:00.000Z","msg":"每次樓價升，我阿媽都會加住客租<br />\n當搵到買家又啱價，就唔會再比租客續<br />\n租有租好，但始終係被動既<br />\n主動權係人手，你根本無真正屬於自己既家"},{"pid":"0fbc4869f52198e0487116bdf876900f13208126","tid":695094,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T03:57:28.000Z","msg":"不如問有幾多人買唔到樓唯有租"},{"pid":"2c2ce3d6d14fa8886889d3be14c7fdfd0d23ee81","tid":695094,"uid":120908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T03:59:49.000Z","msg":"幫人供樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"846f656ef4bf38d0b907951c1f4dad07b26d2fab","tid":695094,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T04:27:29.000Z","msg":"月有陰晴圓缺，遲早實跌一鑊"},{"pid":"c87efad58951f28158bd9839002d055178cb2a87","tid":695094,"uid":13645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd563862fe8a87d01211ad4ef1cdfd3d009bc583","tid":695094,"uid":116709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T03:04:08.000Z","msg":"博樓價跌賺差價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T04:34:01.000Z","msg":"樓價跌到仆街銀行未必咁容易借錢俾你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除非你full paid<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bb58366fc94e5da1dfe9e059d390f1ae4eaf6be","tid":695094,"uid":86097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T07:12:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f3177ad6ce10ed2d724c3b089cbbae180929254f","tid":695094,"uid":86097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T07:13:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"555cda01baa4464996064d91215fbc39f96e9369","tid":695094,"uid":476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T07:14:37.000Z","msg":"支持 越多越好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c7c5f43f255838d5f9f2bbcf864d4056b4eb931","tid":695094